  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Clan</p><p>Prerequisite: Shikigami Clan</p><p>You learn to rapidly craft with paper, even faster than your peers. <br />You gain the following Benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Increase your Intelligence or Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20. </p><p><br />• When you would gain the benefits of a long rest, you may create a number of paper-based items listed within your Papercraft clan feature equal to your proficiency bonus. <br />Due to them being hastily created, they become inert when you would take a short rest. </p><p><br />• Paper based Ninja tools listed within your Papercraft clan feature, has their save DC increase by 1, and deal an additional die of damage.</p>",
